# MiAyudaTIC — Always-On Core

> Neutral OS: `docs/agentic-os.md` | Architecture: `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`

## Identity
- Monorepo: `client/` (React/Vite → Vercel) + `server/` (Node/Express/TS → Render)
- Package manager: **pnpm only**. Never npm or yarn.

## Architecture
Frontend uses **FSD-lite** (`app → pages → features → shared`), backend uses **Feature-modules** (`core/` + `features/` + `shared/`).
Full rules auto-injected when you open `client/` or `server/` files.

## HITL Gates — Ask before proceeding
- Auth, Authorization, or DB schema changes
- Moving files between FSD layers
- Structural refactoring of `client/src/` or `server/src/` root
- Deployment configuration changes
- Installing new dependencies

## Zero Noise Rule
Task is done only when `pnpm build` → 0 errors, 0 unresolved imports, TypeScript clean.
